crypto: drbg - select SHA512

With the swtich to use HMAC(SHA-512) as the default DRBG type, the
configuration must now also select SHA-512.

Fixes: 9b7b94683a9b "crypto: DRBG - switch to HMAC SHA512 DRBG as default
DRBG"
